commit message: Fix blockexplorer url mainnet/testnet switch again
Remove option to determine key creation time
Relax strict mode, as it prevents sending email with attachments on API level 18+ and Android is full of violations itself
No need to save new wallet twice
Make sure wallets always got at least one key
Extract HttpGetThread as top level class
Replace Android SecureRandom class because it has multiple severe bugs that render it useless for cryptographic purposes
